parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of Michelin tires can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Tire blowouts
bulges on the sidewall
tire separation while driving
loss of air pressure
and damage to surrounding vehicle components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inoperative windshield wipers can reduce visibility while driving, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during inclement weather conditions.
symptoms: Windshield wipers are inoperative
motor unit detached from the body
wipers fail to turn on
wipers move erratically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning seat belt can fail to restrain occupants in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: Seat belt is inoperative
unable to latch
seat belt fails to retract
seat belt is stuck.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system defects can cause power failures, circuit breaker trips, and increase the risk of fire, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Power failures
circuit breakers trip
fuses blow
electrical system overheats
electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Structural movement or defects can compromise the overall integrity of the vehicle, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Windshields break due to stress
structural movement
creaking or groaning noises while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Intermittent electrical system failures can cause critical systems to malfunction, leading to safety risks and inconvenience to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The 20 AMP fuse blows intermittently
causing the overhead A/C to fail
and other electrical systems to malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning seat belt can fail to provide proper restraint in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt tightens and won't release
making it difficult or impossible to use.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A warped and misaligned body chassis can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, affecting its safety and performance.
symptoms: The entrance door is out of alignment
making it difficult to lock from the outside
and the dining seat top raises up due to lack of security.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A detached exhaust pipe can cause carbon monoxide to leak into the vehicle, posing a serious health risk to occupants.
symptoms: The exhaust pipe is not attached to the frame of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A stuck toilet valve can cause unpleasant odors and health risks due to sewage exposure.
symptoms: The toilet valve sticks in the open position
leaving the tank exposed or allowing unpleasant odors to enter the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning rearview mirror can obstruct the driver's view, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The rearview mirror moves while driving
obstructing the driver's view.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A cracked or improperly installed windshield can compromise the vehicle's structural integrity and affect visibility.
symptoms: The windshield has stress cracks due to improper installation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling can cause loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle cuts off while driving on several occasions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the slide-out mechanism can cause damage to the vehicle's interior, including carpet and flooring, and potentially lead to water intrusion, which can result in further damage and safety hazards.
symptoms: The slide-out mechanism drags the carpet when used
water leakage in the back slide-out when used.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected engagement of the automatic parking brake can cause the vehicle to suddenly stop or lose control, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The parking brake engages without warning
the parking brake does not release
the vehicle comes to an abrupt stop
the vehicle is unable to move
the parking brake engages while the vehicle is in motion.
